data.description:
Welcome to this 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home that perfectly positioned on a generous lot!  This home is an oasis of tranquility, offering the ideal blend of space and sophistication. From the moment you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of natural light and the elegance of its design. The spacious bedrooms provide a retreat for all family members, and the gourmet kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream.
Whether you're lounging by the fireplace, entertaining in the backyard, or enjoying the countless amenities this home offers, you'll relish every moment spent here.  The roof is brand new, located in a cul-de-sac, close to school, interstate for easy commutes, and dinning options. 
Don't miss the opportunity to make this 4 bedroom haven your own. 
$5,000  allowance being offered towards repairs and upgrades.
